.TH "nvme_init_get_log_supported_log_pages" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_supported_log_pages" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_supported_log_pages \- Initialize passthru command for Supported Log Pages
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_supported_log_pages
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "enum nvme_csi csi "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_supported_log_pages *log "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "csi" 12
Command set identifier, see \fIenum nvme_csi\fP for known values
.IP "log" 12
Array of LID supported and Effects data structures
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_SUPPORTED_LOG_PAGES.
